This program demonstrates how to convert the raw values from an accelerometer to Gs

http://ozzmaker.com/accelerometer-to-g/



Both the BerryIMUv1 and BerryIMUv2 are supported

BerryIMUv1 uses LSM9DS0 IMU
BerryIMUv2 uses LSM9DS1 IMU


Python2 and Python3 supported by this script

Python2;
Run using;
python berryIMU-measure-G.py


Python3;
Run using;
python3 berryIMU-measure-G.py
